        "content": "<p>I'm playing rust_misc_device kmod, and I notice that the dev_info!() shows like this:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">rust_misc_device</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Initialising</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Rust</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Misc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Device</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Sample</span>\n<span class=\"n\">misc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">misc</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">device</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Opening</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Rust</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Misc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Device</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Sample</span>\n<span class=\"n\">misc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">misc</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">device</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Reading</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">from</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Rust</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Misc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Device</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Sample</span>\n<span class=\"n\">misc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">misc</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">device</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Exiting</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Rus